name: Machli Kay Kabab Recipe | Rida Aftab | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Machli Kay Kabab Recipe: Fish (mince) 1 kg Spring Onions 250 gms Green Chilies 6 Red Chilies (crushed) 6 Black Pepper (crushed) 1 tsp Salt 1 tsp Ginger Garlic 1 tbsp Bread (slices) 4 Eggs 4 Garam Masala Powder 2 tsp Mint Leaves Â½ bunch Oil for frying
instructions: In a bowl, add fish mince, crushed black pepper, finely chopped green chilies Add button red chilies, salt, ginger garlic, bread slices, mint leaves Add garam masala powder, eggs, crushed red chilies, green chilies and mix. Now make kabab and fry.
